headline: Why Masco (MAS) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of home-building design and manufacturing company Masco Corporation (NYSE:MAS) jumped 4.1% in the morning session after the company's VP and Chief HR Officer, Jennifer A. Stone, reported acquiring 26,140 shares of company stock.
